        "summary": " For loop in C: solved exercises step by step If you searched for for loop in C solved exercises, this post gives practical patterns that appear in beginner classes and early interview screens.\nThe main goal is to master three key loop patterns: accumulation, counting, and array traversal.\nProblem statement Solve these 4 mini exercises with for:\n",
        "content_html" : "\u003ch2 id=\"for-loop-in-c-solved-exercises-step-by-step\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#for-loop-in-c-solved-exercises-step-by-step\" class=\"header-mark\" aria-label=\"For loop in C: solved exercises step by step\" title=\"For loop in C: solved exercises step by step\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eFor loop in C: solved exercises step by step\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you searched for \u003cstrong\u003efor loop in C solved exercises\u003c/strong\u003e, this post gives practical patterns that appear in beginner classes and early interview screens.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe main goal is to master three key loop patterns: accumulation, counting, and array traversal.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"problem-statement\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#problem-statement\" class=\"header-mark\" aria-label=\"Problem statement\" title=\"Problem statement\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eProblem statement\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSolve these 4 mini exercises with \u003ccode\u003efor\u003c/code\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ecompute the sum \u003ccode\u003e1..n\u003c/code\u003e,\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ecount how many even numbers are in an array,\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003efind the maximum value in an array,\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ecompute the average of an array.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"c-solution\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#c-solution\" class=\"header-mark\" aria-label=\"C solution\" title=\"C solution\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eC solution\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\n    \n    tw-flex \n    tw-flex-row\n    tw-flex-1 \n    tw-justify-between \n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\n    \"\u003e      \n    \u003cbutton \n      class=\"\n        code-block-button\n        tw-mx-2 \n        tw-flex\n        tw-flex-row\n        tw-flex-1\"\n      aria-h