        "id" : "https://rigle.dev/en/ejercicios-c/lista-simplemente-enlazada-en-c-ejercicio-resuelto/",
        "url" : "https://rigle.dev/en/ejercicios-c/lista-simplemente-enlazada-en-c-ejercicio-resuelto/",
        "summary": " Singly linked list in C: solved exercise If you searched for singly linked list in C solved exercise, this example covers real core operations: insert, search, and delete.\nProblem statement Implement a singly linked list with functions to:\ninsert at head, search a value, delete a node, free memory. C solution c\n",
        "content_html" : "\u003ch2 id=\"singly-linked-list-in-c-solved-exercise\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#singly-linked-list-in-c-solved-exercise\" class=\"header-mark\" aria-label=\"Singly linked list in C: solved exercise\" title=\"Singly linked list in C: solved exercise\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eSingly linked list in C: solved exercise\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you searched for \u003cstrong\u003esingly linked list in C solved exercise\u003c/strong\u003e, this example covers real core operations: insert, search, and delete.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"problem-statement\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#problem-statement\" class=\"header-mark\" aria-label=\"Problem statement\" title=\"Problem statement\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eProblem statement\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eImplement a singly linked list with functions to:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003einsert at head,\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esearch a value,\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003edelete a node,\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003efree memory.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"c-solution\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#c-solution\" class=\"header-mark\" aria-label=\"C solution\" title=\"C solution\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eC solution\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\n    \n    tw-flex \n    tw-flex-row\n    tw-flex-1 \n    tw-justify-between \n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\n    \"\u003e      \n    \u003cbutton \n      class=\"\n        code-block-button\n        tw-mx-2 \n        tw-flex\n        tw-flex-row\n        tw-flex-1\"\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u