        "summary": " Doubly linked list in C: solved exercise If you searched for doubly linked list in C solved exercise, this example covers the exact interview and exam pattern: insert nodes, traverse both directions, and free memory correctly.\nProblem statement Implement a doubly linked list where each node contains:\nvalue next pointer prev pointer Create functions to:\n",
        "content_html" : "\u003ch2 id=\"doubly-linked-list-in-c-solved-exercise\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#doubly-linked-list-in-c-solved-exercise\" class=\"header-mark\" aria-label=\"Doubly linked list in C: solved exercise\" title=\"Doubly linked list in C: solved exercise\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eDoubly linked list in C: solved exercise\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you searched for \u003cstrong\u003edoubly linked list in C solved exercise\u003c/strong\u003e, this example covers the exact interview and exam pattern: insert nodes, traverse both directions, and free memory correctly.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"problem-statement\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#problem-statement\" class=\"header-mark\" aria-label=\"Problem statement\" title=\"Problem statement\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eProblem statement\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eImplement a doubly linked list where each node contains:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003evalue\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003enext\u003c/code\u003e pointer\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003eprev\u003c/code\u003e pointer\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCreate functions to:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eappend at the end,\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003etraverse forward,\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003etraverse backward,\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003efree the full list.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"c-solution\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#c-solution\" class=\"header-mark\" aria-label=\"C solution\" title=\"C solution\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eC solution\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\n    \n    tw-flex \n    tw-flex-row\n    tw-flex-1 \n    tw-justify-between \n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\n    \"\u003e      \n    \u003cbutton \n      class=\"\n        code-block-button\n 